{"tid":1857653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西安版“小湯山”醫院開工 最快2月中旬可投入使用","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T13:11:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7f1a77f1bae7ce4fd10935f3412870a843a78e","tid":1857653,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"2月1日，西安版&ldquo;小湯山&rdquo;醫院正式宣佈開工建設。該項目佔地500畝，位於西安市高陵區東南部，首期建設的應急隔離病房將提供500張左右床位。項目地勘和清表等工作目前正在進行，將於2月3日全面開工建設，醫院預計2月中旬可投入使用。截至2月2日10時 ，陝西省累計確診新冠肺炎病例116例，其中，西安市累計確診病例47例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462fd08d238a4f02a932df5740feabf41d274488","tid":1857653,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e023153ec017cbeef00dbdf1ca0c6863a898794","tid":1857653,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819fe18784afebf453513c654d9f618d37e38dbf","tid":1857653,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"驚西 相信黨"},{"pid":"967381797cc5738bbb0da98c6afe75c6e7e5024b","tid":1857653,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"一車車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smi